#: ../../source/index.rst:232
msgid ""
"`rl-rvo-nav (RAL & ICRA2023) <https://github.com/hanruihua/rl_rvo_nav>`_ - "
"Reinforcement learning-based RVO behavior for multi-robot navigation."
msgstr ""
"`rl-rvo-nav（RAL & ICRA2023） <https://github.com/hanruihua/rl_rvo_nav>`_ - "
"基于强化学习的 RVO 行为，用于多机器人导航。"

#: ../../source/index.rst:233
msgid ""
"`RDA_planner (RAL & IROS2023) <https://github.com/hanruihua/RDA_planner>`_ - "
"Accelerated collision-free motion planner for cluttered environments."
msgstr ""
"`RDA_planner（RAL & IROS2023） <https://github.com/hanruihua/RDA_planner>`_ "
"- 面向密集环境的加速无碰撞运动规划器。"

#: ../../source/index.rst:234
msgid ""
"`NeuPAN (T-RO 2025) <https://github.com/hanruihua/NeuPAN>`_ - Direct point "
"robot navigation with end-to-end model-based learning."
msgstr ""
"`NeuPAN（T-RO 2025） <https://github.com/hanruihua/NeuPAN>`_ - 端到端、基于模"
"型学习的点云直接驱动机器人导航。"

