#: ../../source/index.rst:241
msgid ""
"`IRSIM-3DGS-Bridge <https://github.com/Wayneyujie/IRSIM-3DGS-Bridge>`_ - A "
"closed-loop bridge from 3D Gaussian Splatting scenes to IR-SIM planning/"
"following and back to Habitat-GS trajectory playback."
msgstr ""
"`IRSIM-3DGS-Bridge <https://github.com/Wayneyujie/IRSIM-3DGS-Bridge>`_ - 一座"
"闭环桥梁，将三维高斯泼溅（3D Gaussian Splatting）场景接入 IR-SIM 进行规划与跟"
"随，再返回 Habitat-GS 进行轨迹回放。"

